1. *Broj* ljudi koji su se okupili na protestu je bio nevjerovatan. (The number of people who gathered at the protest was unbelievable.)

2. Ona je zapisala *broj* telefona njegove bake. (She wrote down the telephone number of his grandmother.)

3. Ona je primila *broj* počasti za svoje postignuće. (She was given a number of honors for her accomplishment.)

4. Ona je nacrtala *broj* sličica za svoju knjigu. (She drew a number of pictures for her book.)

5. Ja sam našao *broj* odgovora na moje pitanje. (I found a number of answers to my question.)